== Research

Research interests: mathematical optimization, data science, numerical analysis, scientific computing, machine learning, and control

- Derivative-Free Optimization

- AI for optimization

- Approximation theory and neural network approximation

- Model-based trust-region methods

- Subspace methods for large-scale optimization

- Parallel computing and optimization

- Numerical methods for multiple solutions of PDE


